data.description: Welcome home! This beautifully maintained home is ready for YOU! Situated in the desirable Meadows of Heathbrook, this 3 bed 2 bath offers just under 2,000 sqft of living space. Once inside, you'll find an immediate front room, perfect for a formal dining or playroom. Kitchen area overlooks living room, making entertaining and socializing a breeze. Masters quarters offers a spacious arrangement, complete with an office nook and en suite containing his & her vanities and split shower and tub option. Adjoining second and third bedrooms provide ample space and accommodate nicely. Other features include; inside laundry room, finished attic space, new stainless appliances, newer HVAC (2019), fresh exterior paint and the peace of mind of the residence being a one owner home. The gated community provides lit sidewalks & community pool as well as being within walking distance to the Publix at the Heathbrook Commons as well as the surrounding amenities; restaurants, retail, movie theatre, gyms and more! Don't miss your opportunity at SW Ocala's finest living!
